author: Chelsea Todaro
title: Half-eaten fish comes back to life, jumps on plate
text:
This fish knew how to play dead.
Diners in Japan were in for a shock after a half-eaten plate of Sashimi fish tried to jump off the plate, the Daily Mail reports.
>> Read more trending stories
Daily Mail video Sashimi fish comes back to life as it jumps on the plate. In the online video , Japanese diners can be heard screaming when the raw fish starts to wiggle its fins and then miraculously tries to leap off the edge of the plate.
At the end of the clip, the fish makes one more attempt to escape before the cameraman runs away scared and shuts off the footage.
Read more at dailymail.co.uk
